You are building the City Football Rewards Hub -- a demo app for City Football Group showing a fan rewards platform for Man City gaming.

## Key Documents
- `docs/PRD.md` -- Full product requirements (8 screens, tier system, credits economy)
- `DESIGN.md` -- Design system tokens (colors, typography, components, effects)

## Tech Stack
- Vite + React (single-page app)
- Tailwind CSS (utility classes only)
- Lucide React (icons -- no emojis anywhere in the UI)
- Google Fonts: Barlow Condensed (headings) + Barlow (body)
- No backend, no localStorage, no React Router

## Design System (Always Follow)

### Fonts
- Headings: Barlow Condensed -- always uppercase, letter-spacing 0.02em
- Body: Barlow

### Colors
- Background: #0A0E17 (near-black, ALWAYS dark theme)
- Admin Background: #0F1520 (slightly lighter for admin screen)
- Primary CTA: #e6ff00 (Electric Lime) with dark text #001838
- Informational: #6CABDD (Man City Sky Blue) for progress bars, active nav, tier displays
- Secondary: #1C2C5B (Navy)
- Premium: #D4A843 (Gold -- tier badges, credit amounts, premium elements)
- Text: #FFFFFF primary, #8899AA secondary
- Success: #22C55E, Error: #EF4444

### Cards (Glassmorphism)
Always use: `bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/15 rounded-2xl p-6`
Hover: `hover:translate-y-[-2px] hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300`
Featured: add `border-t-2 border-t-[#6CABDD]/50`

### Buttons
- Primary CTA: `bg-[#e6ff00] hover:bg-[#d4eb00] text-[#001838] font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-xl hover:scale-[1.02]`
- Secondary: `bg-[#6CABDD] hover:bg-[#5A9BC9] text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-xl`
- Gold: `bg-[#D4A843] hover:bg-[#C49A3A] text-black font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-xl`
- Ghost: `border border-white/20 text-white hover:bg-white/10 py-3 px-8 rounded-xl`

### Typography
- Landing hero: `text-6xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight`
- Page titles: `text-4xl font-extrabold uppercase tracking-tight`
- Section headers: `text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider`
- Body: `text-sm text-[#8899AA]`
- Credit balance: `text-5xl font-extrabold` with gradient text
- Large numbers: `text-3xl font-extrabold` or gradient text

### Layout
- Left sidebar: 70px fixed, lime active indicator bar
- Right sidebar (dashboard only): 280px fixed
- Main content: offset by sidebars, `p-6`

### Icons
Lucide React only. Monochromatic. No emojis anywhere. Default `w-5 h-5`.

## Tier System
| Tier | Credits | Color |
|------|---------|-------|
| Fan | 0 | White |
| Matchday | 250 | Sky Blue #6CABDD |
| Blue Moon | 1,000 | Royal Blue #2B5BA0 |
| Centurion | 2,500 | Gold #D4A843 |
| Treble | 5,000 | Gold #D4A843 |
| Legend | 10,000 | Gold + Sky Blue gradient |

## Critical Rules
- NEVER use light/white backgrounds
- NEVER use external image URLs
- NEVER use localStorage
- NEVER use React Router -- navigation via useState
- NEVER use emojis -- always Lucide React icons
- ALWAYS use Tailwind utility classes
- ALWAYS use <button> for interactive elements
- ALWAYS use glassmorphism cards with backdrop-blur
- ALWAYS use Barlow Condensed for headings, Barlow for body
- Credits system: totalCreditsEarned (determines tier, never decreases) vs creditBalance (spendable)
- Animations: CSS keyframes only, no framer-motion
- Primary CTA buttons use Electric Lime #e6ff00
